OL,5, Firms are not investing, prices are    
OL,6, rising and the economy is contracting -
OL,7, a dire economic picture that is set to 
OL,8, last into next year, the UK's biggest  
OL,9, business group has warned.             
OL,11,FThe UK could even face a decade of lost
OL,12,Feconomic growth if action is not taken,
OL,13,Fthe Confederation of British Industry  
OL,14,F(CBI) boss Tony Danker said.           
OL,16,F"We don't have people we need, nor the 
OL,17,Fproductivity," said Mr Danker.         
OL,19,FThe CBI expects the economy to contract
OL,20,Fby 0.4% next year.                     
